Then, as inevitable as a storm, came the mother.

She charged forward like a hurricane gone mad.

She did not comfort her crying son first.

She did not ask what had happened.

Instead, she transformed all her panic and fury into a sharpened spear.

Her manicured finger, gleaming beneath salon polish, nearly stabbed into my eye.

“How are you people managing this place?! Is this your so-called guaranteed safety?!”

Accusations crashed over me like a tidal wave.

Parents nearby whispered and pointed.

Every ounce of blame, every fragment of negligence,

was hurled entirely onto my shoulders.

Then the radio at my waist crackled.

<s>It was the boss.</s>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">Inside the office,</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">the boss sat in a leather swivel chair, fingertips pressed together.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">There was no concern in his eyes for the injured child.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">Only calculation.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">Every word was implication.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">Every sentence, a veiled threat.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="color: #DC143C;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">“The store’s reputation cannot be damaged. We have evaluations next month…”</span></span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="color: #DC143C;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">“You were the supervisor today. The morning safety inspection sheet bears your signature…”</span></span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">He wanted the company spotless.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">He wanted every shred of blame pushed onto me—</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">the disposable worker at the very bottom.</span></div>



<div style="margin-left: 10%;"><span style="font-family: 'cocosignum maiuscoletto';">He wanted me to become the perfect scapegoat for a public relations disaster.</span></div>



<div style="width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: 15%; text-align: left; direction: ltr;">
ᕔᙁᗫ Ĭᙁ ꞆዛᕔꞆ ĬᙁꕷꞆᕔᙁꞆ, ᕔԸԸ Ꞇዛꗛ ᗹԸꗞꗞᗫ Ĭᙁ ᙏᎽ ᗹꗞᗫᎽ Ɍꚶꕷዛꗛᗫ ᕓĬꗞԸꗛᙁꞆԸᎽ ĬᙁꞆꗞ ᙏᎽ ꕷꞰꚶԸԸ.<br /><br />
ᎽꗛᕔɌꕷ ꗞꘘ ዛꚶᙏĬԸĬᕔꞆĬꗞᙁ, ᕔᙁǤꗛɌ, ꗛޏᖘԸꗞĬꞆᕔꞆĬꗞᙁ—<br /><br />
ᙅꗞᙏᖘɌꗛꕷꕷꗛᗫ ԸĬꞰꗛ ǤꚶᙁᖘꗞᙡᗫꗛɌ—<br /><br />
ꘘĬᙁᕔԸԸᎽ ᗫꗛꞆꗞᙁᕔꞆꗛᗫ.<br /><br />
“ꞆዛĬꕷ Ĭꕷᙁ’Ꞇ ᙏᎽ ꘘᕔꚶԸꞆ! Ꮍꗞꚶ ᙅꚶꞆ Ꞇዛꗛ ꕷᕔꘘꗛꞆᎽ ĬᙁꕷᖘꗛᙅꞆĬꗞᙁ ᗹꚶᗫǤꗛꞆ Ꞇꗞ ꕷᕔᕓꗛ ᙏꗞᙁꗛᎽ!” Ĭ ꕷᙅɌꗛᕔᙏꗛᗫ ዛᎽꕷꞆꗛɌĬᙅᕔԸԸᎽ.<br /><br />
Ꞇዛꗛ ꚶǤԸĬꗛꕷꞆ ᕔɌǤꚶᙏꗛᙁꞆ ꞆዛᕔꞆ ꗞꘘꘘĬᙅꗛ ዛᕔᗫ ꗛᕓꗛɌ ᙡĬꞆᙁꗛꕷꕷꗛᗫ ꗛޏᖘԸꗞᗫꗛᗫ ᗹꗛꞆᙡꗛꗛᙁ ꚶꕷ.<br /><br />
ዛꗛ ꕷԸᕔᙏᙏꗛᗫ Ꞇዛꗛ ᗫꗛꕷꞰ.<br /><br />
ዛꗛ ᖘꗞĬᙁꞆꗛᗫ ᕔꞆ ᙏᎽ ꘘᕔᙅꗛ ᕔᙁᗫ ꗞɌᗫꗛɌꗛᗫ ᙏꗛ Ꞇꗞ ǤꗛꞆ ꗞꚶꞆ.<br /><br />
Ꞇዛꗛᙁ ዛꗛ ꕷᙁꗛꗛɌꗛᗫ, ꞆዛɌꗛᕔꞆꗛᙁĬᙁǤ Ꞇꗞ ɌꚶĬᙁ ᙏꗛ ᙡĬꞆዛ Ꞇዛꗛ ᙅꗞᙏᖘᕔᙁᎽ’ꕷ ԸꗛǤᕔԸ Ꞇꗛᕔᙏ ꚶᙁꞆĬԸ Ĭ ᙡᕔꕷ ᗹᕔᙁꞰɌꚶᖘꞆ.<br /><br />
ꘘꗛᕔɌ. ᗫꗛꕷᖘᕔĬɌ. ᖘᕔᙁĬᙅ.<br /><br />
ᙏᎽ ᙏĬᙁᗫ ᙡꗛᙁꞆ ᗹԸᕔᙁꞰ.<br /><br />
Ꞇዛꗛ ꘘĬᙁᕔԸ ꞆዛɌꗛᕔᗫ ꗞꘘ Ɍꗛᕔꕷꗞᙁ ꕷᙁᕔᖘᖘꗛᗫ.<br /><br />
Ĭ ǤɌᕔᗹᗹꗛᗫ Ꞇዛꗛ ዛꗛᕔᕓᎽ ᗹɌᕔꕷꕷ ꗞɌᙁᕔᙏꗛᙁꞆ ɌꗛꕷꞆĬᙁǤ ᕔꞆꗞᖘ Ꞇዛꗛ ᗫꗛꕷꞰ—<br /><br />
ᕔ ᙅꗞԸᗫ ᗫꗛᙅꗞɌᕔꞆĬᕓꗛ ᙡꗛĬǤዛꞆ ᙏꗛᕔᙁꞆ Ꞇꗞ ᖘĬᙁ ᗫꗞᙅꚶᙏꗛᙁꞆꕷ Ĭᙁ ᖘԸᕔᙅꗛ—<br /><br />
ᕔᙁᗫ ዛꚶɌԸꗛᗫ ĬꞆ
</div>


<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 'creepster caps';">
Thunk''!''<br /><br />
The arrogance froze upon his face.<br /><br />
His body swayed once, then collapsed to the marble floor.<br /><br />
Blood burst from his temple like a severed pipe,<br /><br />
pouring and pouring,<br /><br />
snaking across the polished stone.<br /><br />
I stood there petrified,<br /><br />
hands trembling violently,<br /><br />
my palms slick with warmth and the metallic smell of blood.<br /><br />
</span></div>


