<span style="font-family: alesand>The balls convulsed.</span>

<span style="font-family: alesand>Collapsed.</span>

<span style="font-family: alesand>Bulged upward,</span>

<span style="font-family: alesand>as if corpses lay packed beneath them.</span>

<span style="font-family: alesand>The souls began to sharpen.</span>

<span style="font-family: alesand>To distort.</span>

